 &lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;/images/shokaX/removeTopFrosted_before.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;移除前&#34; width=&#34;80%&#34; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
